title: AFC Power Rankings: How Many Teams Are Better Than the Chiefs?
description:
Nora and Mal rank the top five teams in the AFC and tell you why other AFC contenders are better than the Chiefs.

Hosts: Nora Princiotti and Mallory Rubin
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
